commit.message:
Fixed rspec for new files_storage configuration
We need to set it to its default value: 'file:///' - same logic as the location configuration
Also we need to put it back to its default value after changing it in the unit tests, as specs are played randomly, if we don't do that, the unit test testing the default value will randomly fail
Merge remote-tracking branch 'origin/master'
